channel.description:
[center][b]Welcome to the Drawing Board.[/b][/center]
Much like [url=http://www.runescape.com]RuneScape's[/url] Draw#Ere Thread, But for the world of MoparScape..
[hr]
Quick Tutorial,
Unlike RuneScape we can use multiple spaces in our forum posts...This is helpful when drawing...
Drawing a basic picture
############## ##### ##### I'm sure you can all probably see teh face there, Myself i'm not great at drawings ### O O ### on computers using letters... #### || #### #### \___/ #### #############
[hr]
# is equal to 2 spaces _ is equal to 1 space - isequal to 1 space 0 is equal to 1 space ¬ is equal to 1 space \ and / are equal to 2 spaces
I'll add more at a later date.
[hr] [b]note;[/b] I Have PMED MoparisTheBest asking him whether we could make this topic sticky if it gets enough interest, I have also asked weather we would be able t have drawing compotitions.
Thanks, WowIlikeTocode
